"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"本周梳理了38个社交平台应用，通过梳理这些平台应用，得出以下观点。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/po63T7XbP6I4EhV3nzL7d.jpg?height=5724&width=2314)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WRDA-NR1laF4uTMtDmQUY.jpg?height=5724&width=2314)\\n\\n1\\\\.不少知名投资机构已经将目光瞄准社交平台。Paradigm、三箭资本、a16z等均已投资社交平台，布局SocialFi赛道。\\n\\n2\\\\.社交平台和社交代币是SocialFi项目中比重较大的两块。社交平台和社交代币项目中，较多项目与NFT、元宇宙相结合。\\n\\n3\\\\.以代币为支撑的社交平台、通证化社区，与当前流行的DAO有相似之处。\\n\\n*Twitter：<https://twitter.com/BitalkNews>*\\n\\n*Telegram：<https://t.me/bitalknews>*\\n\\n*Discord：[discord.com/invite/UDaJ37gwcs](http://discord.com/invite/UDaJ37gwcs)*\",\"timestamp\":1639644748,\"title\":\"社交平台应用\"},\"digest\":\"FB70B5aqC1I1HI-pObRIbFTYYxzt7zTqBFn-ENsHqY4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x21955b6635b67B19Ee0472b8a4Ac4E1d89521cbe\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"GFO7BOR7-jMmGfQPLM1eqF_fNEa5VTIt-vD-qiQkg_Q\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"nc-CV6Fue9Vn5Rn0WHgFCJtkum6320g8BNS3jwzGcP4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"iaDGBoBQL-s6BpfelH8zLQSYDu-I0A_B_3bowaxYcwuZo7om7C11-lcgFhwueV57kbP4eJ3fqOTP9A9z7cHbHQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x97f79a82954fa22c47adc8bfda6e65d08a466537caa264f346b5e21790f6fb5f27df856069c9da20d97e0d4d9c99c84b9d7939d10201bc4b29226980fe5870701c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"GFO7BOR7-jMmGfQPLM1eqF_fNEa5VTIt-vD-qiQkg_Q\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"nc-CV6Fue9Vn5Rn0WHgFCJtkum6320g8BNS3jwzGcP4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"lLMU1r1P16ZQY2c5NuSagI7gksOA8WENEOIWlNf96do\"}"